|WKO=====================================================================
|YKOMoongates connect Darkwind to Dailos, Markas, and Tekal. At the old
Lunar Gate, use |YKBenter dailos|YKO, |YKBenter markas|YKO, or
|YKBenter tekal|YKO. The matching portal chambers in the Plaza of Three
Moons work the same way.

Moon phases change how quickly a gate opens, but never close a route:

  - A visible destination moon provides immediate passage.
  - If the destination is new, the Afterlight Relay borrows light from
    the brightest visible moon. Hold still for 3 seconds.
  - If all three moons are new, the Eclipse Reserve releases stored
    afterlight. Hold still for 8 seconds.

Borrowed and reserve passages cost nothing and use no limited charge.
Moving away, disconnecting, dying, or entering combat before the gate
opens breaks the gathering pattern; simply return and try again.

Look at a lunar gate, portal, or moonstone to see its current phase and
travel mode. Returning from a moon to Darkwind is always immediate.|XX0

